OL,3,CWhy your energy bills could fall this
OL,4,Csummer
OL,6,FThe hot weather the UK has been
OL,7,Fexperiencing over the last month means
OL,8,Fpeople will be using less energy to
OL,9,Fheat their homes, keeping costs down.
OL,11,FPolitical factors include the war in
OL,12,FUkraine, which has impacted gas prices
OL,13,Facross Europe and saw UK energy prices
OL,14,Frise sharply in response.
OL,16,FDonald Trump's announcement of
OL,17,Fsweeping tariffs in April sent the
OL,18,Fmarkets into turmoil, with wholesale
OL,19,Frates plummeting.
