OL,3,CWhy your energy bills could fall this
OL,4,Csummer
OL,6,F"There are, however, reasons for
OL,7,Foptimism. The continued growth of
OL,8,Fdomestically produced renewable energy
OL,9,Fis a positive step forward.
OL,11,F"It improves our energy security and
OL,12,Fhelps mitigate the effects of the
OL,13,Fglobal price shocks we've seen in
OL,14,Frecent years. That progress needs to
OL,15,Fcontinue at pace, not just for the net
OL,16,Fzero transition, but to help build a
OL,17,Fmore stable and secure energy future
OL,18,Ffor all."
