OL,3,CWhy your energy bills could fall this
OL,4,Csummer
OL,6,F"This means summer could be a good
OL,7,Ftime to shop around for fixed deals.
OL,8,FAs a rule of thumb, we'd recommend
OL,9,Flooking for deals cheaper than the
OL,10,Fprice cap, not longer than 12 months
OL,11,Fand without significant exit fees.
OL,13,F"If you are on a fixed deal which will
OL,14,Fbe more expensive than the July price
OL,15,Fcap then it's worth checking your exit
OL,16,Ffees and considering switching if you
OL,17,Fare on a deal with no charges to leave
OL,18,Fearly."
